  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220662921786\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220662921786\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160323_118/isuhani_1458703413264tcGdt_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160323_104212465.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:550px; rheight:550px;\" id=\"20160323_118/isuhani_1458703413264tcGdt_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160323_104212465.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000336088FA3A')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160323_118/isuhani_1458703413264tcGdt_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160323_104212465.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">일주일에 2~3회 내원 하시는 환자분이 계시다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오실때 마다 이렇게 꼭 사오신다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그동안 만두, 찐빵, 과자, 빵, 호빵 등등 사다주셨다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그냥 오셔도 된다 말씀드려도</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">치료 잘 받고 계셔서 감사하다고&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">배고플때 먹으라고 꼭 사다주신다</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">감사합니다 ^^</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
